query: SELECT h.id, h.likes, COUNT(hl.id) as like_count FROM highlights h LEFT JOIN highlight_likes hl ON hl.highlightId = h.id JOIN players p ON p.id = h.playerId WHERE p.fullName LIKE '%Hamza%' GROUP BY h.id, h.likes;
